sentence: Republican Joe Kent is running on a populist platform for a seat in Congress, but first he must win his Washington state GOP primary against incumbent Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler and her corporate donors.
author: Neil Munro
title: Exclusive  Challenger Joe Kent: GOP Incumbent Is Totally Chamber of Commerce'

sentence: Joe Kent, a retired Green Beret who is running to challenge Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler in the Republican primary to represent Washington's 3rd district, shared that the attack "is how the Iranians thank Biden for wanting to get back in the Iran deal."
author: Rebecca Downs
title: Missiles Fired at U.S. Consulate in Iraq Reportedly Came from Iran
